{"tid":2297152,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益）女朋友樓下有大廚煮飯點還擊","createTime":"2020-11-23T05:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T07:50:47.000Z","uid":12269,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b69bcaf4ea31db337ca6830c119bd8fd15d8a71a","tid":2297152,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:25:19.000Z","msg":"搬左過去同居 晚晚都攻到好撚臭<br />\n1.唔肯定邊個單位<br />\n2.私樓<br />\n3.攻到成屋都係味，好重味<br />\n點還拖好<br />\n返到屋企都要比蝦醬咸魚滋擾 <br />\n屌你老母 大廚死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9d12d7a2662f091fc4b4e693165d58383551d7","tid":2297152,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034a8dffb63c99ef3152bd3e5beb313447e6c02f","tid":2297152,"uid":285030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"建議分手"},{"pid":"347097bda8a1b68ee86d4d2b8c335c0a60d754e7","tid":2297152,"uid":314731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:46:44.000Z","msg":"有得屌你就屌啦"},{"pid":"4a117ea4e69f34c2e7e234bd49997ec9beacf9a1","tid":2297152,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"034a8dffb63c99ef3152bd3e5beb313447e6c02f","tid":2297152,"uid":285030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"建議分手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"一個搞著幾層樓，日日硬食油煙。你會唔會話班水貨客一樣比咁多錢搭車，一樣比咁多錢買奶粉，一樣比咁多錢買樓，叫人分手避開佢地。依家係班死大廚累人累物呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa32550d7753873407b86c5f42aba6e09e14ee1d","tid":2297152,"uid":373600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:05:59.000Z","msg":"冇得搞㗎喎，佢煮就山窗囉<br />\n唔通唔俾佢煮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c013ab574ac9821b32bab60a624d8355326267c0","tid":2297152,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"有冇犯法先？"},{"pid":"e3dd43fd714da7725746b1b17900ae32aac3898f","tid":2297152,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fa32550d7753873407b86c5f42aba6e09e14ee1d","tid":2297152,"uid":373600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:05:59.000Z","msg":"冇得搞㗎喎，佢煮就山窗囉<br />\n唔通唔俾佢煮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:23:18.000Z","msg":"不過你會唔會好享受收工返黎想開窗通下風，突然成陣油煙味攻入黎，仲要食撚晒喎<br />\n同時要關窗阻止更多煙入黎，冇得開窗比空氣對流，有撚排散呀，自私撚一個搞幾層"},{"pid":"f096cc31b2ef479e48c716b1a05b8cde11c68e3a","tid":2297152,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c013ab574ac9821b32bab60a624d8355326267c0","tid":2297152,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"有冇犯法先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"所以咪話法例搞唔到你班大廚，但唔代表你班大廚咁做係啱，唔識考慮埋其他人，自私撚<br />\n<br />\n唔應該係屋企煮餸"},{"pid":"b5c3f89df806951a43f6d7291de5bf69cc32ab57","tid":2297152,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:27:26.000Z","msg":"樓主唔post原post link會比真心屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbb4f8ce816938df104fe7333ba3f329910fb57","tid":2297152,"uid":320892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:32:04.000Z","msg":"你煮返啲味俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4271c0285d9e22159fd0af47d174b399ac15509","tid":2297152,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5c3f89df806951a43f6d7291de5bf69cc32ab57","tid":2297152,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:27:26.000Z","msg":"樓主唔post原post link會比真心屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:57:01.000Z","msg":"唔明你講乜"},{"pid":"825d6e183f48e6d84140280d6726992c6bd6dfb6","tid":2297152,"uid":72173,"like":0,"di